Package tech.gitpicard.jcalc

Class JCalculator

  • java.lang.Object
    • tech.gitpicard.jcalc.JCalculator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ASTVisitor
    public final class JCalculator
extends java.lang.Object
implements ASTVisitor
    Evaluates expressions from plain-text source using an abstract syntax tree to support advanced expression syntax such as function calls.
